1790
01:31:16,470 --> 01:31:17,471
Komite Lima?

1791
01:31:17,971 --> 01:31:19,387
Komite untuk Ekonomi Stabil.

1792
01:31:22,721 --> 01:31:24,971
Bangsa ini butuh kepemimpinanmu.

1793
01:31:25,137 --> 01:31:26,971
Kau paham maksudku, Pak?

1794
01:31:30,429 --> 01:31:31,638
Tn. Maguire...

1795
01:31:31,805 --> 01:31:34,597
aku berubah pikiran.
Aku akan berpidato.

1796
